ave to be safe.  We have a password enforcement at work, staff didnt like it but tough.  Students were easily accessing staff accounts!!!! <br /><div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div> <br /><img src="http://common.zam.com/xivsigs/620816.png" height="144" width="482" alt="Signature Image" border="0" /> <br /></div></div>
